<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561917>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Adults and genitalia of Uncobotyodes spp. A–D U. patulalis. A adult, male. B, C male genitalia, slide no. HSQ22214. C cornutus. D female genitalia, slide no. HSQ22223. E–H U. latizona sp. nov. E adult, holotype, male. F, G male genitalia, holotype, slide no. HSQ23354. G cornutus. H female genitalia, paratype, slide no. HSQ23356. Scale bars: 1.0 cm (A, E); 0.5 mm (B, C, F, G); 1.0 mm (D, H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561917/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

